<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>: (الشَّبَج،<span class="c5"> محرَّكَةً:</span> البابُ العالي<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>